parenting, females

00:10:31.560 --> 00:10:33.510
are thus able to abandon them.

00:10:33.510 --> 00:10:35.850
Females can have
multiple births.

00:10:35.850 --> 00:10:38.620
Males are selected to
be as close to females

00:10:38.620 --> 00:10:39.830
as a male can be.

00:10:39.830 --> 00:10:41.900
So there's not a big
difference in size.

00:10:41.900 --> 00:10:44.030
There's not a big difference
in secondary sexual

00:10:44.030 --> 00:10:45.010
characteristics.

00:10:45.010 --> 00:10:46.930
There's not high
levels of aggression.

00:10:46.930 --> 00:10:49.030
There's not big
differences in lifespan.

00:10:49.030 --> 00:10:50.940
Who does a female
want to mate with?

00:10:50.940 --> 00:10:53.770
